n version of the soft phonons identified by the\nX-ray scattering measurements, and a fluctuation of the bond length is\nreflected by the fluctuation of the dCDW formation near the quantum critical\npoint.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 May 2023 04:48:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-19"}
