f our\nmodel over various state-of-the-art recommendation methods. Further visual\nanalysis intuitively explains why our AdaptiveGCL outperforms existing\ncontrastive learning approaches based on selected data augmentation methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 May 2023 09:34:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-19"}
